{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6bb2582686","title":"空军必须迅速组织新部队参战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ce40ddfa37","index":0,"year":1951,"month":11,"day":20,"articleId":"6bb2582686"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"e96ef2527a","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"6bb2582686","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中国人民解放军空军司令员刘亚楼、副政治委员兼政治部主任吴法宪和参谋长王秉章1951年11月19日17时报告的批语。"},{"id":"8a2d33486f","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"6bb2582686","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指刘亚楼等的报告中提出的意见。报告说：根据昨天《人民日报》的消息看来，停战谈判最近可能会有头绪。我们正在设法，更加抓紧时机，尽量求得能使更多的空军部队得到实战锻炼机会，即使稍微冒一点险，也是值得的。具体的方法，就是完成了起码的作战准备工作以后，迅速投入战斗。每个部队不必打得太久，以便让出位置给别的部队去打。"}],"contents":[{"id":"91c8b3fb37","type":"title","text":"空军必须迅速组织新部队参战“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"6bb2582686"},{"id":"e96ef2527a","type":"paragraph","text":"亚楼同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"6bb2582686"},{"id":"8a2d33486f","type":"paragraph","text":"意见很对。必须迅速组织新部队参战，越快越好。圣诞节以前，有停战的极大可能。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"6bb2582686"},{"id":"068313b4f9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"6bb2582686"},{"id":"535c047660","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"6bb2582686"}],"page":{"id":"49625387e7","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"6bb2582686","start":84,"end":84}}}},"__N_SSG":true}